<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HoldOff Affiliate Program — Earn & Grow Together</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Join the HoldOff affiliate program and earn commission for every user you refer.">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1a1f3a 50%, #2d1b4e 100%);
      color: #e0e7ff;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #c4b5fd; }

    nav a {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 1.5rem;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: #a78bfa; }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #93c5fd);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      padding: 12px 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    .features {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    }

    .feature-item h3 {
      color: #a78bfa;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .feature-item p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .form-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #a78bfa;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .form-group textarea {
      resize: vertical;
      min-height: 100px;
    }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #8b5cf6;
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
    }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      margin-top: 4rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #a78bfa;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">HoldOff</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live">Home</a>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Earn With Us</h1>
    <p>Join our affiliate program and earn generous commissions for every user you refer. Help people respect themselves while building your own income stream.</p>
    <button class="cta-btn" onclick="document.querySelector('.form-container').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})">Apply Now</button>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature-item">
      <h3>💰 Competitive Commissions</h3>
      <p>Earn 20% recurring commission on every Plus or Premium subscription you refer, plus 10% on Lifetime purchases. Commissions paid monthly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-item">
      <h3>🎯 Marketing Support</h3>
      <p>We provide you with banners, landing pages, tracking links, and copy to help you promote HoldOff. Everything you need to succeed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-item">
      <h3>📊 Real-Time Dashboard</h3>
      <p>Track your clicks, conversions, and earnings in real time. See exactly how many users signed up from your referrals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-item">
      <h3>👥 Dedicated Support</h3>
      <p>Our affiliate team is here to help you succeed. Questions? We respond within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="form-container">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #a78bfa;">Apply to Become an Affiliate</h2>
    <form method="POST" action="/api/affiliate-apply" id="affiliateForm">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="John Doe">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@example.com">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(555) 123-4567">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="platform">Where will you promote HoldOff? *</label>
        <input type="text" id="platform" name="platform" required placeholder="e.g., Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, Blog, Email List, etc.">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="followers">Estimated Audience Size *</label>
        <input type="text" id="followers" name="followers" required placeholder="e.g., 50k followers, 10k subscribers">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="about">Tell us about your audience *</label>
        <textarea id="about" name="about" required placeholder="Who are your followers? What topics do you cover? Why would they love HoldOff?"></textarea>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit Application</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 HoldOff. Made for people who deserve better.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="/affiliate-terms">Affiliate Terms</a>
    </p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('affiliateForm').addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const formData = new FormData(this);
      try {
        const response = await fetch('/api/affiliate-apply', {
          method: 'POST',
          body: formData
        });
        if (response.ok) {
          alert('Thanks for applying! We\'ll review your application and get back to you within 24 hours.');
          this.reset();
        } else {
          alert('Something went wrong. Please try again.');
        }
      } catch (err) {
        console.error(err);
        alert('Error submitting application.');
      }
    });
  </script>
  <script src="/js/floating-companions.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
